## Description {#details}

Encapsulates a DWARF attribute value and all of the data required to describe the attribute value.

This class is designed to be used by clients that want to iterate across all attributes in a <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarfdie">DWARFDie</a>.

Definition at line 24 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/debuginfo/include/llvm/debuginfo/dwarf/dwarfattribute-h">DWARFAttribute.h</a>.
